d2 Nxb5 35. Bxa5 $17) 33... d2 {Black gets in control} 34. Bxd2 Nxd2 (34... Rxd2 $143 35. Re8+ Kf7 36. b7 $14) 35. b7 Rf8 {The mate threat is Rf1 Threatening mate... how?} 36. h3 Nc4 37. Re6 a4 38. Ra6 Ne5 $1 39. Rxa4 Rb8 40. Rb4 (40. Ra8 $142 Nd7 41. Rxb8+ Nxb8 42. Kf2 $19) 40... Kf7 41. Kh2 Ke7 42. Rh4 h6 43. Rb4 Nf7 44. Rg4 g5 45. Re4+ Kf6 46. Rb4 Nd6 47. h4 Rxb7 (47... Nxb7 $6 48. Rb6+ Kf5 49. Kg3 $19) 48. hxg5+ hxg5 49. Ra4 Rb3 50. g3 Nf5 (50... Kf5 51. Ra5+ Kg4 52. Ra4+ Kf3 53. Kh3 $19) 51. g4 Nh4 52. Ra5 Rc3 53. Ra8 Ke5 54. Rf8 Ke4 55. Rf7 Rd3 56. Rf8 Ng6 57. Rf5 Rd5 (57... Rd5 58. Rxd5 Kxd5 $19) (57... Rd2+ 58. Kg3 Nf4 59. Rxg5 Rg2+ 60. Kh4 Rh2+ 61. Kg3 Rh3+ 62. Kf2 Rf3+ 63. Ke1 $19) 0-1


