1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. Qc2 d5 5. e3 c5 6. Nf3 Nc6 7. a3 Bxc3+ 8. bxc3 b6 9. Bd3 O-O 10. cxd5 exd5 11. O-O $6 ({Better is} 11. dxc5 bxc5 12. c4) 11... c4 $1 {Black conquers the central square e4.} 12. Be2 Bg4 13. Re1 Bh5 14. Nd2 $6 ({Better is} 14. e4 $5 Nxe4 15. Bxc4 $1) 14... Bg6 15. Qd1 b5 16. f3 a5 $6 (16... Re8 $1 {controls e4 (Grünfeld).}) 17. e4 $1 dxe4 18. Nxe4 Bxe4 19. fxe4 Nxe4 20. Qc2 f5 21. Bf3 Qf6 22. Rb1 b4 23. cxb4 $2 {White should exchange his weak a-pawn.} ({Correct is} 23. axb4 $1 axb4 24. cxb4 Qxd4+ 25. Be3 {(Grünfeld).}) 23... Qxd4+ 24. Be3 Qd3 25. Qxd3 cxd3 26. b5 Ne5 27. Bxe4 $2 (27. Bd1 d2 28. Rf1 {builds a defence line.}) 27... fxe4 28. Bd4 Nc4 29. Rxe4 Nxa3 $1 {The weakling has fallen.} 30. Re7 Rf4 $1 31. Be5 $1 Nxb1 32. Bxf4 Rd8 33. b6 $1 d2 34. Bxd2 Nxd2 35. b7 Rf8 36. h3 Nc4 37. Re6 a4 38. Ra6 Ne5 39. Rxa4 Rb8 40. Rb4 $6 (40. Ra8 Nd7 41. Rxb8+ Nxb8 42. Kf2 {gives practical chances.}) 40... Kf7 41. Kh2 Ke7 42. Rh4 h6 43. Rb4 Nf7 44. Rg4 g5 45. Re4+ Kf6 46. Rb4 Nd6 47. h4 Rxb7 48. hxg5+ hxg5 49. Ra4 Rb3 50. g3 Nf5 51. g4 Nh4 52. Ra5 Rc3 53. Ra8 Ke5 54. Rf8 Ke4 55. Rf7 Rd3 56. Rf8 Ng6 57. Rf5 Rd5 0-1


