{[%mdl 64]} 1. d4 Nf6 {Opening = E38 - Nimzoindisch-4.c2 /Nimzo Indian-4.c2 Opening = E34 - Nimzoindisch-4.c2 /Nimzo Indian-4.c2} 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. Qc2 c5 (4... d5 5. e3 {0-1 (57) Reti,R-Nimzowitsch,A Berlin 1928 HCL [Fritz 5.00 (5s)]}) 5. e3 {0-1 (57) Reti,R (2550)-Nimzowitsch,A (2550) Berlin 1928 [Fritz 5.00 (5s)]} (5. dxc5 Bxc5 (5... Na6 6. a3 Bxc3+ 7. Qxc3 Nxc5 8. f3 d6 9. b4 Na4 10. Qb3 Bd7 11. e4 O-O 12. Bg5 Qc7 13. Rc1 Rfc8 {½-½ Chekhov,V-Aseev,K/Krumbach op 1991 (13)}) 6. Nf3 Nc6 7. a3 Nd4 8. Nxd4 Bxd4 9. e3 Bxc3+ 10. Qxc3 O-O 11. b4 d5 12. Bb2 dxc4 13. Bxc4 Bd7 14. Rc1 b5 15. Be2 Rc8 16. Qd4 Rxc1+ 17. Bxc1 Qa8 18. Bf3 Bc6 19. Bxc6 Qxc6 {Capablanca,J-Marshall,F/Budapest 1928/½-½ (40)}) 5... d5 $146 (5... O-O 6. a3 Bxc3+ 7. Qxc3 b6 8. dxc5 bxc5 9. b4 d5 10. Bb2 cxb4 11. axb4 dxc4 12. Bxc4 Qb6 13. Nf3 Ba6 14. O-O Bxc4 15. Qxc4 Nbd7 16. Bd4 Qb7 17. b5 Rfc8 18. Qe2 Ne4 19. Ra5 Nd6 20. Qa2 {Korchnoi,V-Browne,W/Buenos Aires 1979/½-½ (79)}) 6. Nf3 Nc6 7. a3 Bxc3+ 8. bxc3 b6 $146 (8... O-O 9. a4 cxd4 10. cxd4 Ne4 11. Be2 Qa5+ 12. Bd2 Nxd2 13. Qxd2 dxc4 14. Bxc4 b6 15. Bb5 Qxd2+ {½-½ Capablanca,J-Nimzovich,A/Berlin 1928 (15)}) 9. Bd3 O-O 10. cxd5 exd5 11. O-O c4 {Keene: '!'} 12. Be2 Bg4 {Keene: '!'} 13. Re1 Bh5 14. Nd2 Bg6 15. Qd1 b5 16. f3 $15 (16. a4 b4 17. cxb4 Nxb4 $15) 16... a5 {Keene: '?!'} (16... Re8 $1) 17. e4 $17 {Keene: '!'} (17. Bf1 Re8 $15) 17... dxe4 18. Nxe4 (18. fxe4 $2 Nxd4 $1) 18... Bxe4 (18... Nxe4 $6 19. fxe4 Bxe4 20. Bxc4 bxc4 21. Rxe4 $14) 19. fxe4 Nxe4 20. Qc2 f5 {Keene: ' ...Nxd4'} 21. Bf3 Qf6 22. Rb1 b4 23. cxb4 {Keene: '?'} (23. axb4 $1 axb4 24. Bxe4 fxe4 25. Be3 $1) 23... Qxd4+ 24. Be3 Qd3 25. Qxd3 cxd3 26. b5 Ne5 27. Bxe4 fxe4 28. Bd4 Nc4 29. Rxe4 Nxa3 30. Re7 {Do you see the mate threat? Keene: '!'} Rf4 {Keene: '!'} (30... Nxb1 $4 31. Rxg7+ Kh8 32. Rg6+ Rf6 33. Bxf6#) 31. Be5 $19 {Keene: '!'} (31. Rxg7+ Kf8 32. Rf1 Rxf1+ 33. Kxf1 d2 $19 34. Ke2 d1=Q+ 35. Kxd1 Rd8 $19) 31... Nxb1 32. Bxf4 Rd8 {[%cal Yd3d2] Black plans d2 Black intends d2} 33. b6 $2 $19 (33. Re1 $142 $5 Nc3 (33... d2 34. Rd1 a4 35. b6 a3 36. b7 a2 37. Be5 Rb8 $1 38. Bxb8 a1=Q $19) 34. Bd2 Nxb5 35. Bxa5 $17) 33... d2 {Black gets in control} 34. Bxd2 Nxd2 (34... Rxd2 $143 35. Re8+ Kf7 36. b7 $14) 35. b7 Rf8 {The mate threat is Rf1 Threatening mate... how?} 36. h3 Nc4 37. Re6 a4 38. Ra6 Ne5 $1 39. Rxa4 Rb8 40. Rb4 (40. Ra8 $142 Nd7 41. Rxb8+ Nxb8 42. Kf2 $19) 40... Kf7 41. Kh2 Ke7 42. Rh4 h6 43. Rb4 Nf7 44. Rg4 g5 45. Re4+ Kf6 46. Rb4 Nd6 47. h4 Rxb7 (47... Nxb7 $6 48. Rb6+ Kf5 49. Kg3 $19) 48. hxg5+ hxg5 49. Ra4 Rb3 50. g3 Nf5 (50... Kf5 51. Ra5+ Kg4 52. Ra4+ Kf3 53. Kh3 $19) 51. g4 Nh4 52. Ra5 Rc3 53. Ra8 Ke5 54. Rf8 Ke4 55. Rf7 Rd3 56. Rf8 Ng6 57. Rf5 Rd5 (57... Rd5 58. Rxd5 Kxd5 $19) (57... Rd2+ 58. Kg3 Nf4 59. Rxg5 Rg2+ 60. Kh4 Rh2+ 61. Kg3 Rh3+ 62. Kf2 Rf3+ 63. Ke1 $19) 0-1


