1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 Bc5 $2 (3... Bb4) (3... g6) 4. Nxe5 $1 (4. a3 {--> Sicobo-Hon}) (4. d3 {--> Guzman-Metge}) (4. Qe2 {--> Rusteau-Hanna}) (4. Bc4 {--> Seitshiro-Martorell}) (4. Bb5 {--> Bauer-Kannenberg}) 4... Nxe5 (4... Bxf2+ $2 5. Kxf2 Nxe5 6. d4 $16 Qf6+ (6... Nc6 7. Be3 d6 8. Bd3 {--> Krasenkov-Nenashev} (8. Be2 {--> Capablanca-Liebenstein})) 7. Kg1 Ng4 8. Qd2 $16) 5. d4 Bxd4 (5... Bd6 $142 6. dxe5 Bxe5 7. f4 {--> Martorelli-Bellia} (7. Bd3 {--> Belkhodja-Ostojic}) (7. Qd3 {--> Geenen-Trevelyan}) 7... Bxc3+ 8. bxc3 Nf6 (8... d6 9. Qd4 $16) 9. e5 Ne4 10. Qd3 (10. Qd5 f5 $16) 10... Nc5 $2 (10... d5 $11) 11. Qd5 Ne6 $2 12. f5 Ng5 $4 13. h4 $1 {--> 1:0 19.move: first computer's partie: M20(USSR)-IBM7020(USA) 1967}) 6. Qxd4 Qf6 $4 {f3 +-} 7. Nb5 $1 Kd8 (7... c6 $8 8. Nd6+ (8. Nc7+ $2 Kd8 9. Nxa8 $2 Nf3+ $19) 8... Ke7 9. Nf5+) 8. Qc5 $1 {f8#,c7} 1-0


